item.title: CVE-2023-0214|2024-08-02T05:02:43.962Z -- skyhigh%20security -- secure%20web%20gateway%20%28swg%29
item.description: A cross-site scripting vulnerability in Skyhigh SWG in main releases 11.x prior to 11.2.6, 10.x prior to 10.2.17, and controlled release 12.x prior to 12.0.1 allows a remote attacker to craft SWG-specific internal requests with URL paths to any third-party website, causing arbitrary content to be injected into the response when accessed through SWG.
